Text: I\'ve seeded 16 copies of this, and will continue to seed for 1 week more.  I\'d hate to see this swarm die out as this is a great series; hopefully people will take over and continue to seed.
This an excellent thing finding this series on the Bay, thanks to all the seeders and leechers for keepin it alive

Thanks so much for sharing and seeding this.  I was first introduced to Oz & James Drink to Britain and fell in love with the series.  I am so excited to get series 1 & 2 now!  I'll continue to seed this for ages.
